NovellVPN support for NetworkManager

It was added by Sureshkumar T <tsureshkumar@novell.com> at Bangalore
on 2006/06/01.

Assumes that you have a running Novell VPN setup installed from official
releases of turnpike and plugins.
See
http://code.google.com/p/turnpike/

Assumes you have installed any of the following packages:
	novell-ipsec-tools
	turnpike
	novell-nortelplugins
	NetworkManager (http://projects.gnome.org/NetworkManager/)

Code released under the GPLv2. See COPYING file in the NetworkManager
directory.
